<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator> "PPON Research Group, Jonkoping University (JTH)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/date> "2026-04-21" .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description> "The Lighting Product Property Ontology (LPPO) v2.0 provides a data dictionary for the properties describing electric lighting products, luminaires and sensing devices used in the construction industry. The ontology has been developed in accordance with SIS-CEN/TS 17623:2021. Version 2.0 replaces opaque GUID-based class identifiers with human-readable, name-derived URIs while preserving the original GUIDs as bppo:hasGUID values for traceability."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/rights> "This ontology is distributed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License."@en .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/source> <https://www.sis.se/en/produkter/it/e-commerce-web-technologies/sis-cents-176232021/> .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> "Lighting Product Property Ontology (LPPO)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "lppo" .
<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo#" .
