_:genid1423 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#hasValue> "The required measurement methods and the calculation methodology are set in the harmonized standard IEC 62471:2009 / CIE S009:2006 „Photobiological safety of lamps and lamp systems“. The standard divides the sources of incoherent optical radiation into four groups: in the Exempt Group (no photobiological risk) and the Risk Groups 1 to 3 with increasing hazard potential."@en .
